{
  "chapter": 23,
  "chapter_summary": "马如龙趁绿雾救回耗尽气力的铁震天，铁震天仍惦记铁全义。回到杂货店后，谢玉宝借铁震天伤势逼问马如龙，并指出只有谢家能治此伤。铁震天看透绝大师等人故意不承认马如龙身份，是为继续掌控局势，遂决定留下助战。谢玉宝得知马如龙身份后先惊疑，继而凭三月相处认定他不是恶人。张老实现身解释行踪，却被马如龙从茅房门闩细节识破说谎，显出“不老实”的一面。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不能把他留在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们一定要回去把他带出来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "现在回去已来不及了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他们要的不是他，是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你还没有落入他们的手里，他们绝不会对付他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这就是你的杂货店？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "床上这个女人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是你的老婆？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不该把我带回这里来，绝对不应该。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我一定要把你带回这里来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "因为这里有个人说不定可以治好你的伤。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "谁能治得好我的伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你实在不该把他带回来的，因为这里根本没有人能治好他的伤，除了谢家的人之外，谁也治不好他的伤。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不是谢家的人，我只不过是这个杂货店的老板娘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我走。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你本来早就应该走了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不能走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我留在这里，他们来找你的时候，我还可以帮你跟他们拼一拼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "找我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他们会来找我！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在他们第一个要找的人是你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你真的认为他们不相信你说的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你认为他们相信！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "绝对相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他们为什么不承认？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为他们如果承认你说的是真话，承认你就是马如龙，他们就得放我走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "既然我们都已落在他们掌握中，谁也逃不了，他们为什么要承认，为什么要放走我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你就是马如龙？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你就是那个阴险恶毒，无恶不作的马如龙？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "不错，我就是马如龙。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我就是那个无恶不作的马如龙。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不是那个马如龙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不是，绝对不是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那个马如龙阴险恶毒，什么事都做得出。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是我跟你在一起已经有三个月零二十一天，我看得出你绝不是个坏人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我没有回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我根本没有出去过，怎么回来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "刚才我在上茅房。",
